                        eins czeichens <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> und er ew doch schon gericht
                        und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, was <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> weinen gepürt und sey das czeichen
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sawmt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sein wöllet, daz im sein weine wider <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>golt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>d<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und tüt
